  "texts": [
    "To address this, we design OptLLM to accept external data files with a predetermined format.",
    "Users may query the system with instructions on from which files each part of the data can be acquired.",
    "Inspired by LangChain foot_1, the data will not be passed to the model to save tokens and further preserve data privacy.",
    "Instead, only the external solver will access the data files in order to calculate the final solutions.",
    "As shown in Figure 4, at each linear layer of the Qwen model, LoRA inserts two trainable lowrank matrices A ∈ R d×r and B ∈ R r×d to approximately optimize the original parameters:"
